  "title": "SENIOR SITE SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Schedule project activities to ensure completion within the schedule</li>\n  <li>Perform site supervision, including planning and  coordinating technical and site issues</li>\n  <li>Lead workers in carrying out site work</li>\n  <li>Participate in meetings with clients/contractors</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Basic Construction Safety Supervisor (BCSS) Certificate is preferred</li>\n  <li>At least 4 years’ experience in general building/civil engineering projects with a high level of complexity</li>\n  <li>Working experience with town council term contract /R&amp;R projects is preferred</li>\n  <li>Strong organizational, communication and people management skills</li>\n  <li>Singaporean &amp; PR only</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Competitive remuneration package commensurate with qualifications will be offered.</strong></p>\n<p>Interested candidates are invited to apply via email with an updated resume, which should include current and expected salaries, date of availability, and a recent photograph in MS Word Format</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br>\nThank you for applying.</p>",
